==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Effluxion
<hw>Ef*flux"ion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Efflux</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of flowing out;
effusion.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which flows out; effluvium;
emanation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Some light <qex>effluxions</qex> from spirit to spirit.</q>
<rj><qau>Bacon.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Effodient</ent>⟦br⟧
